  <article class="entry h-entry hentry category-reviewing tag-china tag-us-china-relations tag-south-china-sea tag-airsea-battle tag-a2ad tag-cooperation tag-chinese-communist-party tag-pacific author-t-greer post-type-text has-main-image clear" id="article-5818faca2e69cfd82f75b68b" data-item-id="5818faca2e69cfd82f75b68b">

